newsitem.title: USA: U.S. bulk millfeeds - Values mixed, supplies vary.
newsitem.headline: U.S. bulk millfeeds - Values mixed, supplies vary.

text.p: Millfeed prices edged lower at several locations in reaction to increased supplies against continued light demand, dealers said.
However, at other locations, supplies for prompt shipment remained tight and prices were unchanged to slightly higher.
The Kansas market is "heating up a little bit," said a Kansas dealer. Feed demand is better but the mills were running about the same level.
Although new-crop corn was available from the southeast United States, dealers said millfeeds were price competitive with the corn.
